title: DDFP 275: The new "America's team"
itunes:title: DDFP 275: The new "America's team"
description:
Shek is joined by Ross Tucker and Handsome Hank to discuss the best and worst case scenario for the 2014 Dallas Cowboys, fantasy football for beginners and debate which franchise really is now America's team. Random musings also include Shek's Megatron impression and a potential new nickname for producer Black Tie.
